---
import ClockIcon from "../assets/icons/clock.svg"
import LocationIcon from "../assets/icons/location.svg"
import JapaneseCastle from "../assets/icons/japanese-castle.svg"
---

<div id="info" class= "info-strip bg-dark border-t border-b border-gray-800 p-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3">
  <div class="info-block border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-gray-800 reveal">
    <ClockIcon class="mb-4 size-8"/>
    <div class="info-label">Horarios</div>
    <div class="info-value">
      Lunes – Sábado<br />12:00 PM – 10:00 PM<br /><br />
      Domingos<br />12:00 PM – 06:00 PM
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="info-block border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-gray-800 reveal">
    <LocationIcon class="mb-4 size-8"/>
    <div class="info-label">Ubicación</div>
    <div class="info-value">
      Av. Alameda Los Cedros 366<br />Chorrillos, Lima<br /><br />
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/51941442899"
        target="_blank"
        style="color:var(--gold);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.85rem;"
        >+51 941 442 899</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="info-block reveal">
    <JapaneseCastle class="mb-4 size-8"/>
    <div class="info-label">Nuestra filosofía</div>
    <div class="info-value">
      Fusión honesta entre la tradición japonesa y los sabores que crecimos
      comiendo en Lima. Cada roll cuenta una historia.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .info-strip {
    background: var(--dark);
  }
  .info-block {
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  .info-block:last-child {
    border-right: none;
  }
  .info-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .info-value {
    font-family: "Noto Serif JP", serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>
